==English==

===Etymology===
[[time|Time]] + [[stamp]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{computing}}: The date and time an event occurred, usually indicated in "human-readable" text, especially when used in a [[log]] to sequentially track events.

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{computing}}: To mark a date/time attribute of a [[file]] or to indicate the date/time in a [[log]] with the processor's current date and time.